The prefered building system is scons under Linux (automake is
currently broken). The system may be built as follows:

Release version:
   scons
   scons install

Windows cross compilation:
   scons mingw64=1

Debug versions may built with the debug=1 flag.

The autoconf file is currently broken.

Plugins:

To build the plugins the following external libraries are needed:

- cfitsio
- tiff
